Rez Ball (2023)

Sydney Freeland Mauricio Mota and Katie Elmore Mota produce the film for Wise Entertainment, Spencer Beighley, Jamal Henderson, and Lebron James for The Springhill Company (“Hustle”), and Nancy Utley for Lake Ellyn Entertainment. It is executive produced by Pete Chernin and Jenno Topping for Chernin Entertainment, Maverick Carter for the Springhill Company, Scott Lumpkin, Freeland, and Harjo.
